Name: Starlaxis Supernova Edition
About the game: Prepare yourself for mind-blowing puzzle strategy in new dimensions! You think Starlaxis is just a small, easy puzzle game? THINK AGAIN! Master breath-taking challenges, win seemingly impossible boss fights, complete multiple missions goals, overcome dozens of enemies, and last but not least: Save EARTH! Features Explosive puzzle/strategy mix with complex game mechanics Story & Endless mode 5 huge worlds, each with 8-9 missions and different goals to accomplish Great graphic design with beatiful backgrounds and 3D spaceships Choose from 4 upgradable starships 6 commanders with their own signature “special moves” Seemingly impossible boss fights, breath-taking challenges, black holes, dozens of enemies, animated cutscenes and much more will entertain you for many hours STEAM FEATURES: Achievements, Trading Cards and Leaderboard No DLC. Get the COMPLETE game when buying it Joypad, mouse & keyboard Support PC-EXCLUSIVE
